headline: Guardians of the grid: Duke Energy celebrates National Lineworker Appreciation Day April 18
summary: On April 18, Duke Energy celebrates National Lineworker Appreciation Day – a day to recognize the service, commitment and sacrifices of lineworkers, team members who are critical to ensuring customers have access to safe and reliable electricity.
